<p><strong>Zero-click searches now make up 64.82% of all Google queries.</strong> That figure climbed from roughly 50% in 2019 and 60% in 2024. AI Overviews appear on 8% of searches and cut position-one click-through rates by 37.5%. Mobile zero-click rates run 26.6 points higher than desktop.</p>
