Source: <a href="https://www.digitalapplied.com/blog/zero-click-search-statistics-2026-complete-data">Digital Applied, 2026</a></p>
<p><strong>23. The mobile-desktop zero-click gap stands at 26.6 percentage points.</strong>
That gap has widened from about 18 points in 2022.
Source: <a href="https://www.digitalapplied.com/blog/zero-click-search-statistics-2026-complete-data">Digital Applied, 2026</a></p>
<p><strong>24. Mobile zero-click rate for informational queries reaches 84%.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.digitalapplied.com/blog/zero-click-search-statistics-2026-complete-data">Digital Applied, 2026</a></p>
